title: Operation Amsterdam (1959 - UK) [WWII drama] multi subs
description:
Operation Amsterdam (1959 - UK)

Drama / History / War
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0053140/


Filmed at IJmuiden and Amsterdam, Noord-Holland, Netherlands

One of the covert operations at the beginning of World War II is enacted in this fast-paced drama about a government approved diamond heist. A Major from the British army joins up with a Dutch diamond expert and another adventurous Dutchman to steal a fortune in diamonds from a bank vault in Amsterdam before the Nazis completely close off the city. The trio are launched under the covering fire of a British battleship in the harbour and then chauffeured into Amsterdam by Anna, one of many people they encounter who could be either friend or foe.
